H1 is a global data company that connects healthcare insights from around the world. Combining research databases from around the world, H1 Explorer will help you make the connections between the scientific research, the authors behind the research, and stay up-to-date with the latest publications from authors of any specialty.

H1 maintains over 10 million healthcare professional profiles globally.
